---
title: BBQ Meatloaves with Shingled Potatoes plus Roasted Broccoli & Scallion Crema
description: Don’t let the name fool you: These meatloaves are nothing like the basic version you grew up eating (sorry not sorry, Mom and Dad!). Ground beef is infused with scallions and BBQ seasoning, then the shaped loaves are covered with a simply irresistible BBQ glaze. Add a side of roasted broccoli and shingled potatoes drizzled with scallion crema, and you may just be calling home to give your parents a cooking lesson!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64ca54d6d1320bb7c7146b32-efc7a595.jpeg
